            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "(Huh? That's Oskar and Leon... That's an unusual combination to see...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sophie's kind of clumsy and prone to mistakes, after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, really? She seems pretty serious and capable to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You think so? It's true that she's gotten a lot better lately, but she was pretty bad before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "She'd make lots of mistakes with alchemy, and she'd say things like \"I messed up again\" while covered in soot."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Huh, I didn't know. Hmm, that's actually a little unexpected..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh no, it's this time already? I should get going soon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Alright. Make sure you buy some vegetables next time!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I will. See you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "(...They're talking about me again.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "(I'm really curious now... Alright, I'm just going to ask about it!)"
        }
    ]
